abstract: I.B.M. reported quarterly earnings that surpassed Wall Street’s expectations, and it raised its profit forecast for the year.

lead_paragraph: I.B.M. reported quarterly earnings that surpassed Wall Street’s expectations, but analysts cautioned against using its results to draw overly broad conclusions about the state of the technology industry.

headline.main: I.B.M. Profits Beat Wall Street Forecasts
